{"tid":553311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雲門從2樓倒塌　住戶爆：二樓民宿擴建結構全改、間接釀災","createTime":"2018-02-07T10:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T12:20:27.000Z","uid":43523,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3be7285836ed38df9a40c6ad81261bdbf1a88d","tid":553311,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"花蓮強震造成多棟大樓傾倒，一名雲門翠堤大樓住戶透露，二樓蓋了民宿，將結構全部改掉。她認為這麼做會影響大樓安全，果然這次就從二樓倒塌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wG7mT5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwG7mT5D.jpg&h=57240af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雲門翠堤。（圖／新聞台）<br />\n<br />\n《中國時報》報導，這名住戶買下雲門翠堤的四樓，當時二樓的民宿便已營業中。原本一層有八戶，民宿業者改成一戶30坪，改建工程進行時還造成漏水。現在她的房貸還沒繳完，房子就沒了。<br />\n<br />\n土木技師公會表示，民宿房間打通擴建，是否動到隔間牆，必須要進一步認定。這次崩塌主因應是大樓承受頻繁的地震，梁柱系統的裂痕是否有作結構性補強。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《三立新聞網》記者也致電該旅店，無人接聽電話。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455f327a6facd57f25cd336b4a89ab58470056eb","tid":553311,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c42da9b4cda03fd65904b15749dae577480eb5","tid":553311,"uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"台灣記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能個負責人響瓦礫入面接電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f7e87c440ecfa8e381d24a19542cf9782a6a08","tid":553311,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T1